From git@z Thu Jan  1 00:00:00 1970
Subject: [PATCH v2 3/4] dt-bindings: phy: rockchip,rk3588-hdptx-phy: Add
 #clock-cells
From: Cristian Ciocaltea <cristian.ciocaltea@collabora.com>
